                    <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                        <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                        <Value>The number of events received by the DFC on channels 17 through 20 summed over 50 range window openings. The four elements of the array correspond to dividing the major frame up into 50 shots. The last element of the array can be 49 or 51 shots depending on the alignment of the range windows with respect to the major frame. Note that these counts are time tag counts and are subject to all the limitations and behaviors associated with time tags (duplicates, FIFO overflows, etc.).  (not EU-converted)</Value>
