                <Attribute name="DODS_EXTRA" type="Container">
                    <Attribute name="Unlimited_Dimension" type="String">
                        <Value>delta_time</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="Description" type="String">
                    <Value>This DFCx_hk is a diagnostic packet (APID 1072, 1088, 1104) that contains some of the parameters normally part of APID 1254, 1264, 1274 (as sequence flag 01).   Also know as the PCE Altimetric Science Data Major Frame described in ICESat-2-MEB-SPEC-0875, section 5.13 Table 19. The data in the group are neither calibrated nor EU-converted, but preserved from ATL01 in order provided diagnostics for TOF processing.</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="data_rate" type="String">
                    <Value>Data within this group are stored at the data rate of the source APID (nominally 50 Hz).</Value>
                </Attribute>
            </Group>
            <Group name="algorithm_science">
                <Dimension name="delta_time" size="21150"/>
                <Dimension name="ds_4bytes" size="4"/>
                <Dimension name="ds_2samples" size="2"/>
                <Int8 name="ds_2samples">
                    <Dim name="/atlas/pce3/algorithm_science/ds_2samples"/>
                    <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                        <Value>DS for 2 bytes</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                        <Value>1</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                        <Value>Dimension Scale</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="valid_min" type="Int8">
                        <Value>1</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="valid_max" type="Int8">
                        <Value>2</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                        <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                        <Value>Dimension scale for an array of 2 samples.</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                </Int8>
                <Int8 name="ds_4bytes">
                    <Dim name="/atlas/pce3/algorithm_science/ds_4bytes"/>
                    <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                        <Value>DS for 4 bytes</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                        <Value>1</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                        <Value>Dimension Scale</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="valid_min" type="Int8">
                        <Value>1</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="valid_max" type="Int8">
                        <Value>4</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                        <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                        <Value>Dimension scale for an array of 4 bytes.</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                </Int8>
                <Float64 name="delta_time">
                    <Dim name="/atlas/pce3/algorithm_science/delta_time"/>
                    <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                        <Value>Elapsed GPS seconds</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="standard_name" type="String">
                        <Value>time</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                        <Value>seconds since 2018-01-01</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                        <Value>Derived via L1B ATBD</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                        <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                        <Value>The time of the first TX pulse in the major frame, relative to the ATLAS SDP GPS Epoch. The ATLAS Standard Data Products (SDP) epoch offset is defined within /ancillary_data/atlas_sdp_gps_epoch as the number of GPS seconds between the GPS epoch (1980-01-06T00:00:00.000000Z UTC) and the ATLAS SDP epoch. By adding the offset contained within atlas_sdp_gps_epoch to delta time parameters, the time in gps_seconds relative to the GPS epoch can be computed.</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                </Float64>
                <Float64 name="gps_time">
                    <Dim name="/atlas/pce3/algorithm_science/delta_time"/>
                    <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                        <Value>GPS seconds at the Major Frame</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                        <Value>seconds</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                        <Value>ATL01/atlas/pcex/a_pmf_algorithm_science</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                        <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                        <Value>GPS seconds at the Major Frame</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="coordinates" type="String">
                        <Value>delta_time</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Map name="/atlas/pce3/algorithm_science/delta_time"/>
                </Float64>
                <Byte name="alt_band_mask">
                    <Dim name="/atlas/pce3/algorithm_science/delta_time"/>
                    <Dim name="/atlas/pce3/algorithm_science/ds_4bytes"/>
                    <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                        <Value>Band Mask</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                        <Value>counts</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                        <Value>ATL01/atlas/pcex/a_pmf_algorithm_science</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                        <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                    </Attribute>
                    <Attribute name="description" type="String">
