                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="valid_max" type="Int8">
                    <Value>1</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                    <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                    <Value>Carrier Phase Data Record (CrPDR) - Deterioration Flag.  0= Carrier Loop Lock Steady   1 = Carrier Loop Lock Unsteady (Measurement data may be deteriorated).  Note: Valid data records (num_valid_slots) will only be included for the amount of SFCs being tracked by the GPSR. If the tracked SFCs &lt; 24, then the remaining unused CSR data fields within the ancillary packet will be zero-filled.</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="coordinates" type="String">
                    <Value>delta_time</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="flag_meanings" type="String">
                    <Value>steady unsteady</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="flag_values" type="Int8">
                    <Value>0</Value>
                    <Value>1</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Map name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/delta_time"/>
                <Map name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/ds_24_slots"/>
            </Int8>
            <Int64 name="carrier_c_int">
                <Dim name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/delta_time"/>
                <Dim name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/ds_24_slots"/>
                <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                    <Value>CRPDR Integer Carrier Cycle Counter</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                    <Value>counts</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                    <Value>ATL01/sc3/gpsr/carrier_phase</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                    <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                    <Value>Carrier Phase Data Record (CrPDR) - Integer Carrier Cycle Counter - Note: At the beginning of each track the integer carrier cycle count starts with 0.  Note: Valid data records (num_valid_slots) will only be included for the amount of SFCs being tracked by the GPSR. If the tracked SFCs &lt; 24, then the remaining unused CSR data fields within the ancillary packet will be zero-filled.</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="coordinates" type="String">
                    <Value>delta_time</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Map name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/delta_time"/>
                <Map name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/ds_24_slots"/>
            </Int64>
            <Float32 name="carrier_c_fract">
                <Dim name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/delta_time"/>
                <Dim name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/ds_24_slots"/>
                <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                    <Value>degrees</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                    <Value>CRPDR Carrier Cycle Fraction</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                    <Value>ATL01/sc3/gpsr/carrier_phase converted</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                    <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                    <Value>Carrier Phase Data Record (CrPDR) - Carrier Cycle Fraction -  Fraction corresponding to 360 degrees divided by 4096.  Note: Valid data records (num_valid_slots) will only be included for the amount of SFCs being tracked by the GPSR. If the tracked SFCs &lt; 24, then the remaining unused CSR data fields within the ancillary packet will be zero-filled.</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="coordinates" type="String">
                    <Value>delta_time</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Map name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/delta_time"/>
                <Map name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/ds_24_slots"/>
            </Float32>
            <Int8 name="channel_num">
                <Dim name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/delta_time"/>
                <Dim name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/ds_24_slots"/>
                <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                    <Value>CRPDR Channel Number</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                    <Value>counts</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                    <Value>ATL01/sc3/gpsr/carrier_phase</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="valid_min" type="Int8">
                    <Value>0</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="valid_max" type="Int8">
                    <Value>23</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                    <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                    <Value>Carrier Phase Data Record (CrPDR) - Channel Number. 0 to 23;  All other values invalid.  Note: Valid data records (num_valid_slots) will only be included for the amount of SFCs being tracked by the GPSR. If the tracked SFCs &lt; 24, then the remaining unused CSR data fields within the ancillary packet will be zero-filled.</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="coordinates" type="String">
                    <Value>delta_time</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Map name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/delta_time"/>
                <Map name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/ds_24_slots"/>
            </Int8>
            <Int8 name="sv_id">
                <Dim name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/delta_time"/>
                <Dim name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/ds_24_slots"/>
                <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                    <Value>CRPDR Space Vehicle ID</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                    <Value>counts</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                    <Value>ATL01/sc3/gpsr/carrier_phase</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="valid_min" type="Int8">
                    <Value>0</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="valid_max" type="Int8">
                    <Value>32</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                    <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                    <Value>Carrier Phase Data Record (CrPDR) - Space Vehicle ID. (0 = No signal acquisition or tracking;  1-32 = GPS SVs. All other values invalid).  Note: Valid data records (num_valid_slots) will only be included for the amount of SFCs being tracked by the GPSR. If the tracked SFCs &lt; 24, then the remaining unused CSR data fields within the ancillary packet will be zero-filled.</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="coordinates" type="String">
                    <Value>delta_time</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Map name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/delta_time"/>
                <Map name="/gpsr/carrier_phase/ds_24_slots"/>
            </Int8>
            <Attribute name="DODS_EXTRA" type="Container">
                <Attribute name="Unlimited_Dimension" type="String">
                    <Value>delta_time</Value>
                    <Value>ds_24_slots</Value>
                </Attribute>
            </Attribute>
            <Attribute name="Description" type="String">
                <Value>Contains parameters related to the GPSR Carrier Phase Data Record (CrPDR).</Value>
            </Attribute>
            <Attribute name="data_rate" type="String">
                <Value>Data within this group are stored at the data rate of the source Spacecraft Ancillary Science Data Packets. (nominally one per second.)</Value>
            </Attribute>
        </Group>
        <Group name="channel_status">
            <Dimension name="delta_time" size="423"/>
            <Dimension name="ds_24_slots" size="24"/>
            <Int8 name="ds_24_slots">
                <Dim name="/gpsr/channel_status/ds_24_slots"/>
                <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                    <Value>DS for 24 slots</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                    <Value>1</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                    <Value>Dimension Scale</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="valid_min" type="Int8">
                    <Value>1</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="valid_max" type="Int8">
                    <Value>24</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                    <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                    <Value>Dimension scale representing each of the 24 slots.</Value>
                </Attribute>
            </Int8>
            <Float64 name="delta_time">
                <Dim name="/gpsr/channel_status/delta_time"/>
                <Attribute name="long_name" type="String">
                    <Value>Elapsed GPS seconds</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="standard_name" type="String">
                    <Value>time</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="units" type="String">
                    <Value>seconds since 2018-01-01</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="source" type="String">
                    <Value>Derived via Time Tagging</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="contentType" type="String">
                    <Value>referenceInformation</Value>
                </Attribute>
                <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                    <Value>Time, in seconds since the ATLAS SDP GPS Epoch, computed from raw_gps_time_sec and subseconds in the time correlation group. The ATLAS Standard Data Products (SDP) epoch offset is defined within /ancillary_data/atlas_sdp_gps_epoch as the number of GPS seconds between the GPS epoch (1980-01-06T00:00:00.000000Z UTC) and the ATLAS SDP epoch. By adding the offset contained within atlas_sdp_gps_epoch to delta time parameters, the time in gps_seconds relative to the GPS epoch can be computed.</Value>
                </Attribute>
            </Float64>
            <Int8 name="code_loop_bw">
                <Dim name="/gpsr/channel_status/delta_time"/>
                <Dim name="/gpsr/channel_status/ds_24_slots"/>
