                <Attribute name="description" type="String">
                    <Value>Channel Status Record (CSR) - Logical Tracking State - Single Frequency Channel 1-24. See Appendix C within DN-ICESAT2-SYS-024 for enumerated values. Note: num_valid_slots indicate the number of channel that actual valid to use.  the remaining unused data fields are zero-filled.</Value>
